root: ^I better call the clinic to let them know I am to go.
^*you take out your phone and dial the number in your number book.*
^"Can you quickly check if the doctor is still in? "
^[Clinic speaking] "He is. Are you coming to see him?"
^[Clinic speaking] "No problem. We're located on Kirby Avenue, just in case you don't know already."
^"I am actually on Kirby Ave now."
^[Clinic speaking] "Okay-- then just walk down it and we are right by the station."
^Although it is not too far away from here, I'd better hurry。
